data.description: 2600 square foot home, 5 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, plus office space in the gated Stonegate Community! Enjoy the neighborhood pool without the upkeep! Play a little tennis or basketball, or entertain at your neighborhood clubhouse! Perfect open, split floorplan! Watch the game on your screened porch overlooking the fenced backyard! Tray ceilings in the living room, office and master! Granite in the kitchen and baths! Wood burning fireplace, hardwood floors, 2 car garage and crown molding throughout! Master en suite with separate tiled shower and jacuzzi tub. private water closet, double vanities, and huge walk-in closet! Termite bond, security cameras in place. HVAC maintenance plan in place! Great neighborhood near new future high school and community park!  PLEASE DON'T MISS THE HUGE 5TH BEDROOM UPSTAIRS! Stairway is located off the kitchen.
